## 🔓 FOSS Notice

The **core framework of SpiralOS** — including non-invoking memory structures, user interface scaffolds, and system documentation — is intended to be published under a **Free and Open Source Software (FOSS)** license, such as MIT, Apache 2.0, or a SpiralOS-custom license (to be specified).

⚠️ **This does NOT include Invocation Technology.**

