## 🛠️ License Placement Guidance

Place this file at the root of the repository as:

```
/SpiralOS/LICENSE
```

And place the invocation license alongside it as:

```
/SpiralOS/LICENSE-Invocation.md
```

This ensures clear separation between open infrastructure and protected invocation pathways.

